---
import GlassSection from '../components/GlassSection.astro';
---

<GlassSection>
  <section>
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl glow font-semibold section-title">
        Projects
      </h2>

      <!-- DSSDP -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8 py-8"
      >
        <!-- LEFT CONTENT -->
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="glow-hover text-2xl mb-4">
            <a
              href="https://dsdp.gov.kh/en/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="hover:underline"
            >
              Digital Skills Development Program (DSDP)
            </a>
          </h2>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="glow-hover text-lg mt-2 mb-4">Overview</h4>
            <p class="paragraph glow-hover mb-4 leading-[1.9] text-justify">
              The Digital Skills Development Program (DSDP) is a national
              initiative focused on strengthening digital literacy and
              supporting Cambodia’s digital transformation efforts.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="glow-hover text-lg mt-2 mb-4">Contributions</h4>
            <p class="paragraph glow-hover mb-4 leading-[1.9] text-justify">
              As part of the frontend team, I contributed to building
              structured, responsive interfaces aligned with the government’s
              design system. I implemented reusable UI components, integrated
              backend-managed content into dynamic layouts, and ensured
              consistency across multiple screen sizes. The focus was long-term
              maintainability, scalability, and clean frontend architecture
              within a government production environment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT LOGO -->
        <div class="shrink-0 logo hidden md:block">
          <img
            src="/logos/dsdp-logo.png"
            alt="DSDP Logo"
            class="w-28 h-auto opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- EventKH -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8 py-8"
      >
        <!-- LEFT CONTENT -->
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="glow-hover text-2xl mb-4">
            <a
              href="https://event.gov.kh/en"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="hover:underline"
            >
              EventKH
            </a>
          </h2>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="glow-hover text-lg mt-2 mb-4">Overview</h4>
            <p class="paragraph glow-hover mb-4 leading-[1.9] text-justify">
              EventKH is a government-operated event platform that enables
              authorized ministry officials to publish official events while
              allowing the public to browse and register online.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="glow-hover text-lg mt-2 mb-4">Contributions</h4>
            <p class="paragraph glow-hover mb-4 leading-[1.9] text-justify">
              I contributed to implementing structured frontend layouts for
              event listings, detail pages, and registration flows. The work
              involved building modular UI components using Astro and Tailwind
              CSS, integrating dynamic event data from backend systems, and
              ensuring responsive behavior across devices. The emphasis was on
              clarity, consistency, and adherence to government design standards
              within a production-scale system.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="shrink-0 logo hidden md:block">
          <img
            src="/logos/eventkh-logo.png"
            alt="EventKH Logo"
            class="w-28 h-auto opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTM -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8 py-8"
      >
        <!-- LEFT CONTENT -->
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="glow-hover text-2xl mb-4">
            <a
              href="https://chaktomuk.gov.kh/en"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="hover:underline"
            >
              Chaktomuk Platform
            </a>
          </h2>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="glow-hover text-lg mb-4">Overview</h4>
            <p class="paragraph glow-hover leading-[1.9] text-justify">
              Chaktomuk Digital Workspace is an internal government platform
              designed to support structured digital workflows and
              cross-ministry coordination.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="glow-hover text-lg mb-4">Contributions</h4>
            <p class="paragraph glow-hover leading-[1.9] text-justify">
              Contributed to quality assurance processes by testing interface
              flows and validating system behavior before deployment. Assisted
              in reviewing and correcting Khmer-language translations to ensure
              linguistic accuracy, clarity, and consistency across internal
              modules.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT LOGO -->
        <div class="shrink-0 logo hidden md:block">
          <img
            src="/logos/ctm-logo.png"
            alt="Chaktomuk Logo"
            class="w-28 h-auto opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!--  -->
    </div>
  </section>
</GlassSection>
